<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>MarkUp - Grupo 13</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      align-items: center;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #f1f5f9;
      display: flex;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    main { max-width: 680px; padding: 40px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .badge {
      background: #1e293b;
      border: 1px solid #334155;
      border-radius: 20px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4.5rem); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    h1 span { color: #38bdf8; }
    p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 auto 36px; max-width: 500px; }
    a {
      background: #38bdf8;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: #0f172a;
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover { background: #7dd3fc; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <div class="badge">Grupo 13 · GCEIC26</div>
    <h1>Mark<span>Up</span></h1>
    <p>Calcule o preço de venda ideal, analise o lucro real e descubra o ponto de equilíbrio do seu negócio.</p>
    <% if (user) { %>
      <a href="<%= basePath %>/calculo">Abrir cálculo</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <a href="<%= basePath %>/login">Entrar no sistema</a>
    <% } %>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
